
    "I've seen things you people wouldn't believe. Attack ships on fire
    off the shoulder of Orion. I watched C-beams glitter in the dark
    near the Tannhäuser Gate. All those moments will be lost in time,
    like tears in rain. Time to die."

.i rau da zo'u tu'e mi pu'i zgana da poi do krici lo du'u ke'a na ka'e
fasnu .i lo gunta kesyblo pu se jelspo ne'a lo janco be fi la'e la'oi
.Orion .i mi pu viska lo nu lo gusli'i cu mircai ne'i lo manku re'o la'e
la'oi .Tannhäuser. po'u lo vorme .i da ba se claxu tai da'i lo se klaku
ne'i lo carvi .i ca zi mrobi'o


# {tu'e} is to scope the {rau da}s so they can be tears-in-rain'd
"I've seen things you people wouldn't believe"
.i mi pu'i zgana da poi do krici lo du'u ke'a na ka'e fasnu
"enough" somethings: ( I can-and-has observe somethings that you believe the fact-that it not capable happen

# things being "on fire" in space might be tricky, and throwing rocks is
# likely more practical (per F = mv^2) if less poetical than that which
# glitters. anyways...
"Attack ships on fire off the shoulder of Orion"
.i lo gunta kesyblo pu se jelspo ne'a lo janco be fi la'e la'oi .Orion
attack spaceboat past burn next to the shoulder-of-Orion

# TODO might instead {la'oi C-beams} which would be shorter? and maybe
# quote in all of "Tannhäuser Gate"
"I watched C-beams glitter in the dark near the Tannhäuser Gate"
.i mi pu viska lo nu lo gusli'i cu mircai ne'i lo manku re'o la'e la'oi .Tannhäuser. po'u lo vorme
I past see the event of line-of-light glitter within the dark adjacent to Tannhäuser which is the gate

# TODO something better for "lost in time" than {claxu}? but did not see
# anything that jumped out at me while poking through the dictionary
"All those moments will be lost in time, like tears in rain"
.i da ba se claxu tai da'i lo se klaku ne'i lo carvi
somethings future lacks like the tears within the rain

# TODO could instead be {.i nau mrobi'o} ?
"Time to die"
.i ca zi mrobi'o
now soon die

# (the closing {tu'u} is not present, making the {tu'e} unclosed. this
# may bother lisp people more than others
